Company Overview
Robert Walters Jakarta was established in 2012 and due to continual expansion is seeking highly entrepreneurial, motivated recruitment consultants to grow the business. Jakarta is one of the worlds largest cities, is internationalising rapidly, with a corresponding increase in demand for an international standard of recruitment services.Robert Walters is one of the world's leading global specialist recruitment and recruitment outsourcing businesses. The Group specialises in permanent and contract recruitment across all industry sectors, and count FORTUNE 500 companies, investment banks and multinational blue-chip commercial organisations as clients. Operating at all levels of seniority, Jakarta - Indonesia office manages the careers of the best professionals in the following disciplines: commerce finance, banking & financial services, engineering, human resources, legal, information technology, sales & marketing, supply chain, procurement & logistics, and support and administration fields. The world's leading education publishing company is looking for a Higher & Professional Education Consultant in Jakarta.  Reporting to the Sales Manager, you will be responsible for seeking new business opportunities as well as maintaining relationship with clients.
